description_0: A wooden carving of a bird is hanging from a tree branch facing the bottom right corner of the image. The bird is attached by three small chain links attached to a strip of wood, the strip of wood is attached to three more chain links that are attached to the tree. The bottom of the image is covered with leaves and branches going across the image. A branch is extending diagonally from the right side to the top of the image. The clear blue sky is visible in the middle and right of the image, there is no cloud coverage visible.
description_1: An extreme close up view of a Praying Mantis on a rough textured tree trunk. The tree trunk is dark brown, black, and gray. It has deep crevices. The trunk takes up two thirds of the right side of the frame. In the center of the tree trunk is the Praying Mantis. It has camouflaged itself to be the same colors as the bark. it looks like a stick with legs. The legs look like stick figure legs. The praying hands, it's known for, are indistinguishable. Its head is a short horizontal crossbar. The left third of the frame is a large tree with a blue sky. This portion of the frame is blurry.
